A national AI-powered smart water management system designed to reduce water waste, optimize irrigation, and monitor real-time consumption.
The system integrates:

Mobile app for citizens, farmers, and industries.

IoT sensors to detect leaks, measure soil moisture, and track water flow.

AI algorithms to optimize agricultural irrigation and predict abnormal consumption.

Smart payment integration for seamless billing.

Wastewater monitoring to enhance recycling and reuse.

By combining AI, IoT, and Big Data, the project provides a sustainable, efficient, and scalable solution to tackle Egyptâ€™s water scarcity challenge.
